sfMondongoPlugin
================

Mondongo is the simple, powerful and ultrafast Object Document Mapper (ODM) for PHP (5.3.0+) and MongoDB.

sfMondongoPlugin is the plugin to use Mondongo with Symfony.

Installation
------------

    ./symfony plugin:install -s beta sfMondongoPlugin

Documentation
-------------

  * [Mondongo](http://mondongo.es/documentation/0.9/reference/en)
  * [sfMondongoPlugin](http://mondongo.es/documentation/0.9/sf-mondongo-plugin/en)

